#: ../../helpers_guide.rst:4
msgid ""
"Pollywog provides a collection of helper functions to simplify common "
"calculation patterns. These functions can generate either complete "
"``Number`` or ``Category`` objects for your ``CalcSet``, or return just "
"the expression/logic for use in more complex calculations."
msgstr ""

